'''Plex'''是一套[[媒體播放器|媒體播放器]]及{{le|媒體伺服器|Media server}}軟件，讓用戶整理在裝置上的[[有聲書|有聲書]]、[[音樂|音樂]]、[[播客|播客]]、[[圖片|圖片]]和[[视频|影片]]檔案，以供[[串流|串流]]至[[流動裝置|流動裝置]]、[[智能電視|智能電視]]和{{le|電子媒體播放器|Digital media player}}上。Plex可用於[[Microsoft_Windows|Windows]]、[[Android|Android]]、[[Linux|Linux]]、[[OS_X|OS X]]和[[FreeBSD|FreeBSD]]<ref name="Gigaom">{{cite web |url=http://gigaom.com/video/plex-laika-myplex/ |title=Plex gets Windows client, cloud service, media sharing |date=2011-10-31 |first=Janko |last=Roettgers |website=[[Gigaom|Gigaom]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121208070629/http://gigaom.com/video/plex-laika-myplex/ |archivedate=2012-12-08 |accessdate=2016-03-27 }}</ref>。另外，Plex亦讓用戶透過該平台觀看來自[[YouTube|YouTube]]、[[Vimeo|Vimeo]]和[[TED大會|TED]]等內容提供商的影片。Plex亦與{{le|Bitcasa|Bitcasa}}、[[Box公司|Box]]和[[Dropbox|Dropbox]]等雲端服務兼容<ref>{{cite web |url=https://plexapp.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/201342573-Cloud-Sync-Storage-Provider-Setup |title=Cloud Sync Storage Provider Setup – Plex |publisher=Zendesk |date= |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archive-date=2014-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305214120/https://plexapp.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/201342573-Cloud-Sync-Storage-Provider-Setup |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/plex/id383457673 |title=Plex on the App Store on iTunes |publisher=Apple |date=2014-07-31 |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archive-date=2014-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140829172932/https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/plex/id383457673 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

用戶可透過Plex[[前端和後端|前端]]媒體播放器「Plex Media Player」管理及播放在一台運行「Plex Media Server」的遠端電腦上的多媒體檔案。另外，用戶可使用「Plex Online」服務以社群開發的插件收看[[Netflix|Netflix]]、[[Hulu|Hulu]]和[[CNN|CNN]]的影片。<ref name="CrunchGear Interview">{{cite web |url=http://www.crunchgear.com/2010/01/15/interview-we-talk-to-the-lead-developer-of-plex-media-center-for-mac-os-x-it-was-doing-boxee-like-stuff-before-boxee-was-cool/ |title=CrunchGear Interview: We talk to the lead developer of Plex Media Center for Mac OS X: It was doing Boxee-like stuff before Boxee was cool |date=2010-01-15 |first=Nicholas |last=Deleon |website=CrunchGear |accessdate=2016-03-27 |archive-date=2010-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100118083235/http://www.crunchgear.com/2010/01/15/interview-we-talk-to-the-lead-developer-of-plex-media-center-for-mac-os-x-it-was-doing-boxee-like-stuff-before-boxee-was-cool/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

Plex的媒體播放器本來是基於[[Kodi|Kodi]]（當時名為「XBMC」）的[[原始碼|源碼]]開發<ref name="theverge.com">http://www.theverge.com/2012/12/24/3801306/plex-desktop-app-rebranded-as-plex-home-theater-adds-airplay-in {{Wayback|url=http://www.theverge.com/2012/12/24/3801306/plex-desktop-app-rebranded-as-plex-home-theater-adds-airplay-in |date=20160327052918 }} Plex desktop app rebranded as Plex Home Theater</ref>，在2008年5月21日[[複刻|分支]]。直至2015年10月，Plex使用的軟件才完全被[[專有軟件|專有軟件]]取代<ref name="CrunchGear Interview"/><ref>https://blog.plex.tv/2015/10/20/introducing-the-plex-media-player/ {{Wayback|url=https://blog.plex.tv/2015/10/20/introducing-the-plex-media-player/ |date=20160320150450 }} Introducing the Plex Media Player</ref><ref name="XBMC for Mac">{{cite web |url=http://xbmc.org/forum/showpost.php?p=186843&postcount=13 |title=XBMC for Mac forked for a separate project called PLEX (formerly known as "OSXBMC") |date=2008-05-23 |website=XBMC Community Forum |accessdate=2009-03-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090821031959/http://xbmc.org/forum/showpost.php?p=186843&postcount=13 |archivedate=2009-08-21 }}</ref><ref name="Thinking inside the box">{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2009/oct/07/boxee-web-video-software |title=Thinking inside the box |date=2009-10-07 |first=Kevin |last=Anderson |website=Guardian |accessdate=2016-03-27 |archive-date=2012-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026030239/http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2009/oct/07/boxee-web-video-software |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Plex的伺服器軟件「Plex Media Server」是由專有軟件組成，與由[[自由軟件|自由軟件]]組成的Kodi不同。

